  "texts": [
    "Third, Gen AI output, especially creative forms (text, images), can infringe on IPR, with consequent risks for Gen AI creators and users.",
    "The Gen AI research agenda that we propose covers three broad areas (1) Gen AI input, (2) Gen AI output, and (3) concerns associated with Gen AI.",
    "The topics contained within this research agenda warrant consideration by academic researchers, firms that create Gen AI applications, Gen AI users, and policy experts.",
    "Gen AI already has exerted notable impacts on marketing; it will continue to have substantially more impact in the days and years ahead, and there is much still to learn.",
    "We hope that this agenda motivates, and structures continued research into Gen AI."
